---
// Blog index - AGENTES by Luminari
---
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Blog — AGENTES by Luminari</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Artículos sobre agentes AI, automatización y productividad para negocios." />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <script defer src="https://umami.luminari.agency/script.js" data-website-id="9a5bb1d1-9bc1-417a-8b4b-72b44044d168"></script>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    :root {
      --green: #25D366;
      --green-light: #e8faf0;
      --green-lighter: #f0fdf5;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --gray-200: #e5e7eb;
      --gray-400: #9ca3af;
      --gray-500: #6b7280;
      --gray-600: #4b5563;
      --gray-800: #1f2937;
      --gray-900: #111827;
    }
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif;
      background: var(--white); color: var(--gray-800);
      line-height: 1.6; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }
    nav {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
    }
    nav .inner {
      max-width: 1120px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; height: 64px;
    }
    .logo { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.15rem; color: var(--gray-900); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
    .logo span { color: var(--green); }
    nav .links { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 28px; }
    nav .links a { text-decoration: none; color: var(--gray-600); font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.9rem; transition: color .2s; }
    nav .links a:hover { color: var(--gray-900); }
    nav .links .cta-nav {
      background: var(--green); color: white; padding: 8px 20px; border-radius: 100px;
      font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.85rem;
    }
    nav .links .cta-nav:hover { color: white; }

    .page {
      max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 140px 24px 100px;
      min-height: 80vh;
    }
    .page h1 {
      font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--gray-900);
      margin-bottom: 12px; letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }
    .page .sub { color: var(--gray-500); font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 48px; }

    .empty {
      text-align: center; padding: 80px 20px;
      background: var(--green-lighter); border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(37,211,102,0.15);
    }
    .empty .icon { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .empty h2 { font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gray-900); margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .empty p { color: var(--gray-500); font-size: 0.95rem; }

    footer {
      padding: 40px 0; text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
      color: var(--gray-400); font-size: 0.82rem;
    }
    footer a { color: var(--green); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <div class="inner">
    <a href="/" class="logo"><span>◆</span> AGENTES</a>
    <div class="links">
      <a href="/blog">Blog</a>
      <a href="/#empezar" class="cta-nav">Empezar</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<main class="page">
  <h1>Blog</h1>
  <p class="sub">Ideas, guías y novedades sobre agentes AI para negocios.</p>
  <div class="empty">
    <div class="icon">✍️</div>
    <h2>Próximamente</h2>
    <p>Estamos preparando contenido increíble. Vuelve pronto.</p>
  </div>
</main>

<footer>
  <div><a href="/">◆ AGENTES</a> by Luminari &copy; 2026</div>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
